INSERT INTO [dbo].[FactProperty]
    (ParcelKey, BuildingKey, ZoningKey, CompanyKey, PersonKey,
     ValuationAmount, AreaSqM, Floors, HeightM,
     LastTransactionDate, YearBuilt, LoadDate)
SELECT
    dp.ParcelKey,
    db.BuildingKey,
    dz.ZoningKey,
    dc.CompanyKey,
    dpe.PersonKey,
    sb.valuation_amount,
    sp.area_sq_m,
    sb.floors,
    sb.height_m,
    sp.last_transaction_date,
    sb.year_built,
    SYSDATETIME() AS LoadDate
FROM [dbo].[stg_Parcels] sp
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[DimParcel] dp 
    ON dp.CadastralCode = sp.cadastral_code
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[stg_Buildings] sb
    ON sb.parcel_id = sp.parcel_id
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[DimBuilding] db
    ON db.PermitNumber = sb.permit_number
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[stg_Zoning] sz
    ON sz.zoning_code = sp.zoning_code
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[DimZoning] dz
    ON dz.ZoningCode = sz.zoning_code
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[stg_Companies] sc
    ON sc.company_id = sp.owner_id
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[DimCompany] dc
    ON dc.CompanyName = sc.company_name
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[stg_People] sppl
    ON sppl.person_id = sp.owner_id
LEFT JOIN [dbo].[DimPerson] dpe
    ON dpe.FullName = sppl.full_name;
